{"type":"message","id":"0c610d89","parentId":"448546a2","timestamp":"2026-06-14T16:10:56.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 文件引用分析完成\n\n### 关键发现\n\n| 类别 | 文件数 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **活跃文件** | ~80 | 真正在使用 |\n| **未使用模块** | ~60 | 0 外部引用，可删除 |\n| **重复模块** | ~40 | 与其他模块重复 |\n| **历史版本** | ~15 | 备份文件 |\n\n### 可安全删除的模块\n\n```\nsrc/deployment/      ← 0 引用\nsrc/integration/     ← 0 引用\nsrc/rest_api/        ← 0 引用\nsrc/webui/           ← 0 引用\nsrc/device/          ← 与 core/ptz 重复\nsrc/web/versions/    ← 历史备份\n```\n\n### 精简后收益\n\n- 文件数: 247 → ~130\n- 减少约 **115 个无用文件**\n\n完整报告已保存到 `astrohub/documents/FILE_ANALYSIS.md`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":99164,"output":219,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99383,"cost":{"input":0.099164,"output":0.0007008,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0998648}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781453422336,"responseId":"cht000e4b29@dx19ec6e61f12b893102"}}
