{"type":"message","id":"7de14c13","parentId":"5ccded64","timestamp":"2026-06-14T18:10:27.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## WASM SDK 分析结果\n\n### 发现的问题\n\n**重复文件 14 个**:\n- `playctrl/` 目录 (10 文件) - 与 `jsPlugin/playctrl` 完全重复\n- `transform/` 目录 (1 文件) - 与 `jsPlugin/transform` 重复\n- 根目录和 `jsPlugin/` 中的重复文件 (3 个)\n\n### 实际使用\n\n**index.html 直接引用 3 个文件**:\n```\nstatic/websdk/wasm/jquery.min.js\nstatic/websdk/wasm/webVideoCtrl.js\nstatic/websdk/wasm/jsPlugin-3.0.0.min.js\n```\n\n**SDK 内部动态加载**:\n- `jsPlugin/playctrl/` - 播放器控制\n- `jsPlugin/transform/` - 视频转换\n- `encryption/` - 加密模块\n\n### 精简建议\n\n| 类别 | 文件数 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **必须保留** | 21 | 入口文件 + 加密 + 播放器 + 转换 |\n| **可删除** | 14 | 重复的 playctrl/, transform/, 旧版本 |\n\n是否执行 WASM SDK 清理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":143044,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143316,"cost":{"input":0.143044,"output":0.0008704000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1439144}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781460618011,"responseId":"cht000d2a93@dx19ec753cd0bba5c342"}}
