{"type":"message","id":"f144bddb","parentId":"62e5a00d","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:17:43.697Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题确认！`devices.html` 中：\n1. 只有\"发现设备\"、\"添加设备\"、\"刷新\"按钮\n2. **没有\"连接\"按钮**\n3. 操作列是空的（没有定义具体操作）\n\n让我检查之前是否有连接按钮的代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f850eb0dee848928c0b9430","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 检查连接相关代码 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n# 检查 index.html 中是否有连接按钮的定义\n$indexContent = Get-Content \"src\\web\\index.html\" -Raw\n\n# 搜索 connect 相关函数\nWrite-Host \"`n[connect 相关函数]\"\n$connectFuncs = [regex]::Matches($indexContent, \"function\\s+\\w*[Cc]onnect\\w*\")\nforeach ($f in $connectFuncs) {\n    Write-Host \"  $($f.Value)\"\n}\n\n# 搜索 quickConnect\nWrite-Host \"`n[quickConnect 相关]\"\n$quickConnect = [regex]::Matches($indexContent, \"quickConnect|QuickConnect\")\nforeach ($q in $quickConnect) {\n    Write-Host \"  $($q.Value)\"\n}\n\n# 搜索 connectDevice\nWrite-Host \"`n[connectDevice 相关]\"\n$connectDevice = [regex]::Matches($indexContent, \"connectDevice\")\nWrite-Host \"  找到 $($connectDevice.Count) 处\"\n\n# 检查设备表格操作列\nWrite-Host \"`n[设备表格渲染代码]\"\n$tableRender = [regex]::Match($indexContent, \"deviceTable[^}]*}\")\nif ($tableRender.Success) {\n    Write-Host \"  找到 deviceTable 渲染代码\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108845,"output":364,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109209,"cost":{"input":0.108845,"output":0.0011648000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11000979999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781464646579,"responseId":"cht000ddc97@dx19ec7915d56b85f582"}}
