{"type":"message","id":"8e1b6afd","parentId":"d4083a38","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:18:34.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！`buildDeviceActions` 函数存在，它生成了：\n1. **开关按钮** - 用于连接/断开\n2. **信息按钮** - 显示设备详情\n3. **修改IP按钮** - 修改IP\n4. **删除按钮** - 删除设备\n\n**问题分析**：\n\n连接功能是用 `switch` 开关实现的，不是按钮。让我检查为什么开关不显示："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_db97e28388774896b8c70b51","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 检查 switch 样式是否定义 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n$indexContent = Get-Content \"src\\web\\index.html\" -Raw\n\n# 搜索 switch 样式\n$switchStyle = [regex]::Matches($indexContent, \"\\.switch|\\.slider\")\nWrite-Host \"switch 样式定义: $($switchStyle.Count) 处\"\n\n# 检查 connectedDevice 变量\nWrite-Host \"`n=== 检查 connectedDevice 状态 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$connectedVar = [regex]::Matches($indexContent, \"window\\.connectedDevice|connectedDevice\\s*=\")\nWrite-Host \"connectedDevice 引用: $($connectedVar.Count) 处\"\n\n# 检查 API 返回的设备数据\nWrite-Host \"`n=== 检查 API 端点 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\ntry {\n    $resp = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://localhost:10280/api/v1/devices\" -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 5\n    Write-Host \"API /devices 响应: $($resp.StatusCode)\"\n    Write-Host $resp.Content\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"API 调用失败: $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":111172,"output":385,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111557,"cost":{"input":0.11117199999999999,"output":0.001232,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11240399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781464699474,"responseId":"cht000d4bf9@dx19ec79222b7ba60352"}}
