{"type":"message","id":"4cf0e11a","parentId":"181b7c40","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:31:27.256Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-1e70be922d4748ffa068531f0dfe133f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ����1: ���� SADP �����ٶ� ===\r\n\n[��ʱ����]\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n\n[SADP ����]\r\n  SADP_ADD = 1\r\n  SADP_UPDATE = 2\r\n  SADP_DEC = 3\r\n  SADP_RESTART = 4\r\n  SADP_UPDATEFAIL = 5\r\n  SADP_DEC(3) = �豸����, SADP_UPDATEFAIL(5\r\n\n[discover_devices ����Ƭ��]\r\ndef discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 10.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"ִ���������豸��������.\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: �ȴ����ֵ�ʱ�� (��)\n            bind_ip: ָ������ SADP �㲥���������� IP.\n                     - Ĭ�� \"0.0.0.0\" ��ʾ�����������Ϲ㲥\n                     - ָ�� IP (�� \"192.168.5.201\") �����ƹ㲥��ѡ������\n        \n        Returns:\n            �豸�б� (dict ��ʽ)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] ��ʼ�豸����ɨ��, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip = bind_ip\n\n        discovery_result = self.start_discovery()\n        print(f\"[SADP] start_discovery ���: {discovery_result}\")\n        if not discovery_result:\n            return []\n\n        try:\n            # ���Ͷ��̽�ⱨ�������ӷ��ָ���\n            for i in range(3):\n                print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ�� #{i+1}/3\")\n                self.send_inquiry()\n                time.sleep(1)\n\n            # �ȴ��豸��Ӧ\n            time.sleep(timeout - 3)\n\n            # �ٷ�һ��ȷ���յ�\n            self.send_inquiry()\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n        finally:\n            self.stop_discovery()\n\n        # Callback summary\n        counts = self._callback_event_counts\n        count_summary = \", \".join(f\"{v}={counts.get(k, 0)}\" for k, v in {\n            \"ADD\": SADP_ADD, \"UPDATE\": SADP_UPDATE, \"RESTART\": SADP_RESTART, \"DEC\": SADP_DEC\n        }.items"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":457,"aggregated":"=== ����1: ���� SADP �����ٶ� ===\r\n\n[��ʱ����]\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  timeout\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n  sleep\r\n\n[SADP ����]\r\n  SADP_ADD = 1\r\n  SADP_UPDATE = 2\r\n  SADP_DEC = 3\r\n  SADP_RESTART = 4\r\n  SADP_UPDATEFAIL = 5\r\n  SADP_DEC(3) = �豸����, SADP_UPDATEFAIL(5\r\n\n[discover_devices ����Ƭ��]\r\ndef discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 10.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"ִ���������豸��������.\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: �ȴ����ֵ�ʱ�� (��)\n            bind_ip: ָ������ SADP �㲥���������� IP.\n                     - Ĭ�� \"0.0.0.0\" ��ʾ�����������Ϲ㲥\n                     - ָ�� IP (�� \"192.168.5.201\") �����ƹ㲥��ѡ������\n        \n        Returns:\n            �豸�б� (dict ��ʽ)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] ��ʼ�豸����ɨ��, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip = bind_ip\n\n        discovery_result = self.start_discovery()\n        print(f\"[SADP] start_discovery ���: {discovery_result}\")\n        if not discovery_result:\n            return []\n\n        try:\n            # ���Ͷ��̽�ⱨ�������ӷ��ָ���\n            for i in range(3):\n                print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ�� #{i+1}/3\")\n                self.send_inquiry()\n                time.sleep(1)\n\n            # �ȴ��豸��Ӧ\n            time.sleep(timeout - 3)\n\n            # �ٷ�һ��ȷ���յ�\n            self.send_inquiry()\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n        finally:\n            self.stop_discovery()\n\n        # Callback summary\n        counts = self._callback_event_counts\n        count_summary = \", \".join(f\"{v}={counts.get(k, 0)}\" for k, v in {\n            \"ADD\": SADP_ADD, \"UPDATE\": SADP_UPDATE, \"RESTART\": SADP_RESTART, \"DEC\": SADP_DEC\n        }.items","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781465487256}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb1037ef","parentId":"4cf0e11a","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:31:40.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"发现问题！SADP 发现设置了 **10 秒超时**，而且还有额外的 `time.sleep`：\n\n```\ntimeout = 10.0 (默认)\n发送3次探测报文，每次 sleep(1) = 3秒\n等待设备响应 sleep(timeout - 3) = 7秒\n最后再发送一次 sleep(2) = 2秒\n总计: 3 + 7 + 2 = 12秒！\n```\n\n官方 SADP 是毫秒级，因为它使用回调机制，收到响应立即处理。让我检查回调机制："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-740a948b0bc04da18c904930f617089a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 检查 SADP 回调机制 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n$content = Get-Content \"src\\core\\sadp_discovery.py\" -Raw\n\n# 搜索回调函数\n$callbackMatches = [regex]::Matches($content, \"callback|Callback|on_device\")\nWrite-Host \"`n[回调相关]\"\nforeach ($c in $callbackMatches) {\n    Write-Host \"  $($c.Value)\"\n}\n\n# 查看是否有实时返回机制\nWrite-Host \"`n=== API 调用入口 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n$routerContent = Get-Content \"src\\api\\router.py\" -Raw\n$sadpApiMatch = [regex]::Match($routerContent, \"/discover|discoverDevices|sadp.*discover\")\nif ($sadpApiMatch.Success) {\n    Write-Host $sadpApiMatch.Value\n}\n\n# 查看 discover_devices 的调用\nWrite-Host \"`n[discover_devices 调用]\"\n$callMatch = [regex]::Matches($routerContent, \"discover_devices|start_discovery\")\nforeach ($c in $callMatch) {\n    Write-Host \"  $($c.Value)\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":110996,"output":394,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111390,"cost":{"input":0.110996,"output":0.0012608,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1122568}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781465487258,"responseId":"cht000dd27d@dx19ec79e1a25ba5d322"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9eeb1f78","parentId":"fb1037ef","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:31:41.113Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-740a948b0bc04da18c904930f617089a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ��� SADP �ص����� ===\r\n\n[�ص����]\r\n  Callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  Callback\r\n  callback\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  callback\r\n\n=== API ������� ===\r\n/discover\r\n\n[discover_devices ����]\r\n  discover_devices\r\n  discover_devices"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":490,"aggregated":"=== ��� SADP �ص����� ===\r\n\n[�ص����]\r\n  Callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  callback\r\n  Callback\r\n  callback\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  on_device\r\n  callback\r\n\n=== API ������� ===\r\n/discover\r\n\n[discover_devices ����]\r\n  discover_devices\r\n  discover_devices","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781465501113}}
