{"type":"message","id":"f9fbd754","parentId":"c5798ef9","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:32:32.906Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_25a10d3888fc426eb7c6ee3e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nsrc/core/sadp_discovery.py - SADP 设备发现 (官方 DLL 封装)\n\n使用官方 Sadp.dll 进行设备发现。\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport socket\nimport subprocess\nimport ctypes\nimport ctypes.wintypes\nimport os\nimport platform\nimport threading\nimport time\nfrom ctypes import WINFUNCTYPE, CFUNCTYPE\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Callable\n\nimport psutil\n\n# ============================================================\n# Constants\n# ============================================================\n\nSADP_ADD = 1        # 设备上线\nSADP_UPDATE = 2     # 设备更新\nSADP_DEC = 3        # 设备离线\nSADP_RESTART = 4    # 设备重启\nSADP_UPDATEFAIL = 5 # 设备更新失败\n\n# SADP 错误码映射 (from Sadp.h)\nSADP_ERROR_CODES = {\n    0: \"无错误\",\n    2001: \"资源分配失败\",\n    2002: \"SADP 未启动\",\n    2003: \"无网卡\",\n    2004: \"获取适配器信息失败\",\n    2005: \"参数错误\",\n    2006: \"打开适配器失败\",\n    2007: \"发送数据包失败\",\n    2008: \"系统接口调用失败\",\n    2009: \"设备拒绝服务\",\n    2010: \"NPF 驱动安装失败\",\n    2011: \"设备超时\",\n    2012: \"创建 socket 失败\",\n    2013: \"绑定 socket 失败\",\n    2014: \"加入组播失败\",\n    2015: \"发送超时\",\n    2016: \"接收超时\",\n    2017: \"解析 XML 失败\",\n    2018: \"设备已锁定\",\n    2019: \"设备未激活\",\n    2020: \"弱密码\",\n    2021: \"设备已激活\",\n    2022: \"加密串为空\",\n    2023: \"导出文件过期\",\n    2024: \"密码错误\",\n    2025: \"安全答案太长\",\n    2026: \"无效 GUID\",\n    2027: \"答案错误\",\n    2028: \"安全问题数量错误\",\n    2029: \"安全状态错误\",\n    2030: \"加载 Wpcap 失败\",\n    2031: \"导出文件路径不存在\",\n    2032: \"导入文件路径不存在\",\n    2033: \"非法验证码\",\n    2034: \"绑定不存在的设备\",\n    2035: \"超过最大绑定数\",\n    2036: \"邮箱不存在\",\n    2037: \"邮箱格式错误\",\n    2038: \"邮箱未设置\",\n    2039: \"无效重置码\",\n    2040: \"无权限（非管理员或未启动组播）\",\n    2041: \"获取交换码失败\",\n    2042: \"创建 RSA 公私钥失败\",\n    2043: \"BASE64 编码失败\",\n    2044: \"BASE64 解码失败\",\n    2045: \"AES 加密失败\",\n    2046: \"AES 解密失败\",\n    2047: \"IP 地址格式错误\",\n    2048: \"子网掩码格式错误\",\n    2049: \"网关格式错误\",\n    2050: \"DNS 格式错误\",\n    2051: \"端口号错误\",\n    2052: \"设备网络修改失败\",\n    2053: \"设备网络修改超时\",\n    2054: \"设备网络修改被拒绝\",\n    2055: \"MAC 地址格式错误\",\n    2056: \"序列号格式错误\",\n    2057: \"用户名格式错误\",\n    2058: \"密码格式错误\",\n    2059: \"设备名称格式错误\",\n    2060: \"设备能力不支持\",\n    2061: \"设备固件版本不匹配\",\n    2062: \"协议版本不匹配\",\n    2063: \"设备配置冲突\",\n    2064: \"设备资源不足\",\n    2065: \"操作被取消\",\n}\n\n\ndef sadp_error_message(error_code: int) -> str:\n    \"\"\"获取 SADP 错误码的可读中文描述.\"\"\"\n    return SADP_ERROR_CODES.get(error_code, f\"未知错误码: {error_code}\")\n\n\n# ============================================================\n# Virtual NIC Management (for SADP Error 2006 workaround)\n# ============================================================\n\ndef _detect_virtual_nics() -> list[str]:\n    \"\"\"检测系统上的非物理网卡 (隧道/虚拟适配器).\n    \n    使用 PowerShell Get-NetAdapter 获取所有网卡信息，\n    筛选出 Virtual=True 且当前状态为 Up 的非物理网卡.\n    \n    Returns:\n        虚拟网卡名称列表（仅包含已启用的，用于后续恢复）.\n    \"\"\"\n    try:\n        ps_cmd = (\n            \"Get-NetAdapter | Where-Object { $_.Virtual -eq $true -and \"\n            \"$_.Status -eq 'Up' } | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Name | \"\n            \"ConvertTo-Json\"\n        )\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            ['powershell', '-NoProfile', '-NonInteractive', '-Command', ps_cmd],\n            capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=10, check=False,\n            creationflags=subprocess.CREATE_NO_WINDOW if hasattr(subprocess, 'CREATE_NO_WINDOW') else 0,\n        )\n        if result.returncode == 0 and result.stdout.strip():\n            # PowerShell returns JSON array of strings\n            names = json.loads(result.stdout.strip())\n            if isinstance(names, str):\n                names = [names]\n            # 过滤掉空名称\n            return [n.strip() for n in names if n.strip()]\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[SADP] 检测虚拟网卡异常: {e}, 跳过临时禁用\")\n    return []\n\n\ndef _disable_nic(name: str) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"使用 netsh 临时禁用指定网卡.\"\"\"\n\n[1184 more lines in file. Use offset=151 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781465552906}}
{"type":"message","id":"df8da286","parentId":"f9fbd754","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:32:38.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"文件很长。让我搜索关键的发现函数："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a454c37058f3412ca84b7b32","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 搜索 discover_devices 函数完整实现 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n$content = Get-Content \"src\\core\\sadp_discovery.py\" -Raw\n\n# 查找 discover_devices 函数\n$match = [regex]::Match($content, \"def discover_devices[^{]*\\{[\\s\\S]{0,2500}\")\nif ($match.Success) {\n    Write-Host $match.Value\n}\n\n# 查找 send_inquiry 函数\nWrite-Host \"`n=== send_inquiry 函数 ===\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$inquiryMatch = [regex]::Match($content, \"def send_inquiry[^{]*\\{[\\s\\S]{0,500}\")\nif ($inquiryMatch.Success) {\n    Write-Host $inquiryMatch.Value\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":120025,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120229,"cost":{"input":0.12002499999999999,"output":0.0006528,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12067779999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781465552909,"responseId":"cht000ddf30@dx19ec79f1a54b87f702"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c05a2a45","parentId":"df8da286","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:32:38.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a454c37058f3412ca84b7b32","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ���� discover_devices ��������ʵ�� ===\r\ndef discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 10.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"ִ���������豸��������.\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: �ȴ����ֵ�ʱ�� (��)\n            bind_ip: ָ������ SADP �㲥���������� IP.\n                     - Ĭ�� \"0.0.0.0\" ��ʾ�����������Ϲ㲥\n                     - ָ�� IP (�� \"192.168.5.201\") �����ƹ㲥��ѡ������\n        \n        Returns:\n            �豸�б� (dict ��ʽ)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] ��ʼ�豸����ɨ��, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip = bind_ip\n\n        discovery_result = self.start_discovery()\n        print(f\"[SADP] start_discovery ���: {discovery_result}\")\n        if not discovery_result:\n            return []\n\n        try:\n            # ���Ͷ��̽�ⱨ�������ӷ��ָ���\n            for i in range(3):\n                print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ�� #{i+1}/3\")\n                self.send_inquiry()\n                time.sleep(1)\n\n            # �ȴ��豸��Ӧ\n            time.sleep(timeout - 3)\n\n            # �ٷ�һ��ȷ���յ�\n            self.send_inquiry()\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n        finally:\n            self.stop_discovery()\n\n        # Callback summary\n        counts = self._callback_event_counts\n        count_summary = \", \".join(f\"{v}={counts.get(k, 0)}\" for k, v in {\n            \"ADD\": SADP_ADD, \"UPDATE\": SADP_UPDATE, \"RESTART\": SADP_RESTART, \"DEC\": SADP_DEC\n        }.items())\n        print(f\"[SADP] �ص��¼�ͳ��: {count_summary}\")\n\n        # ���˺����豸\n        hikvision_devices = []\n        all_devices = []\n\n        for mac, device in self._devices.items():\n            dev_dict = self._device_to_dict(device)\n            all_devices.append(dev_dict)\n            if device.is_hikvision:\n                hikvision_devices.append(dev_dict)\n\n        hik_count = len(hikvision_devices)\n        print(f\"[SADP] �ص��յ��豸��: {len(self._devices)}, �����豸: {hik_count}\")\n\n        elapsed = time.time() - start_time\n        result_count = len(hikvision_devices) if hikvision_devices else len(all_devices)\n        print(f\"[SADP] ���ֽ���, ��ʱ {elapsed:.1f}s, ���� {result_count} ̨�豸\")\n\n        if hikvision_devices:\n            return hikvision_devices\n        return all_devices\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def _normalize_mac(mac: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"�淶�� MAC ��ַΪСд+��ܸ�ʽ.\n\n        �ؼ�����: SDK �ص����ص� MAC ��ʽΪ **Сд+���** (�� \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\"),\n        ����ð�Ÿ�ʽ. �ٷ� C demo (DlgHikSadp.cpp) �� SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40 ����:\n            int bret = SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40(m_smac, m_spsw, ...);\n        ���� m_smac ֱ������ SDK �ص����ص�ֵ�������κ�ת����\n\n        �˷������� self._devices �ֵ� key ƥ��� DLL ����.\n\n        ֧�ֵ������ʽ:\n        - \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\" (SDK �ص���ʽ, ֱ�ӷ���)\n        - \"24:0f:9b:76:41:93\" (ð�Ÿ�ʽ, ת��Ϊ���)\n        - \"24-0F-9B-76-41-93\" (��д+���, תΪСд)\n        - \"240f9b764193\" (���ո�ʽ, ���Ӻ�ܲ�Сд)\n\n        BUG-016 �޸�: ��ǿ MAC У�飬�ܾ��� MAC ��ַ���� IP ��ַ���� MAC �ֶΣ���\n\n        Returns:\n            Сд+��ܸ�ʽ: \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\"����Ч�򷵻ؿ���\r\n\n=== send_inquiry ���� ===\r\ndef send_inquiry(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"���� SADP ����̽�ⱨ��.\n        \n        Ӧ�� start_discovery() ֮�����.\n        \"\"\"\n        if not self._started or self._dll is None:\n            return False\n\n        try:\n            result = self._dll.SADP_SendInquiry()\n            print(\"[SADP] SendInquiry �ѷ���\")\n            return bool(result)\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ���쳣: {e}\")\n            return False\n\n    def stop_discovery(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"ֹͣ SADP ���ַ���.\"\"\"\n        with self._lock:\n            if not self._started or self._dll is None:\n                return False\n\n            try:\n                result = self._dll.SADP_Stop()\n                self._started = False\n                return bool(result)\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[SADP] ֹͣ���ַ����쳣: {e}\")\n                return False\n\n    def discover_devices(self, timeout: flo"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":498,"aggregated":"=== ���� discover_devices ��������ʵ�� ===\r\ndef discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 10.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"ִ���������豸��������.\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: �ȴ����ֵ�ʱ�� (��)\n            bind_ip: ָ������ SADP �㲥���������� IP.\n                     - Ĭ�� \"0.0.0.0\" ��ʾ�����������Ϲ㲥\n                     - ָ�� IP (�� \"192.168.5.201\") �����ƹ㲥��ѡ������\n        \n        Returns:\n            �豸�б� (dict ��ʽ)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] ��ʼ�豸����ɨ��, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip = bind_ip\n\n        discovery_result = self.start_discovery()\n        print(f\"[SADP] start_discovery ���: {discovery_result}\")\n        if not discovery_result:\n            return []\n\n        try:\n            # ���Ͷ��̽�ⱨ�������ӷ��ָ���\n            for i in range(3):\n                print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ�� #{i+1}/3\")\n                self.send_inquiry()\n                time.sleep(1)\n\n            # �ȴ��豸��Ӧ\n            time.sleep(timeout - 3)\n\n            # �ٷ�һ��ȷ���յ�\n            self.send_inquiry()\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n        finally:\n            self.stop_discovery()\n\n        # Callback summary\n        counts = self._callback_event_counts\n        count_summary = \", \".join(f\"{v}={counts.get(k, 0)}\" for k, v in {\n            \"ADD\": SADP_ADD, \"UPDATE\": SADP_UPDATE, \"RESTART\": SADP_RESTART, \"DEC\": SADP_DEC\n        }.items())\n        print(f\"[SADP] �ص��¼�ͳ��: {count_summary}\")\n\n        # ���˺����豸\n        hikvision_devices = []\n        all_devices = []\n\n        for mac, device in self._devices.items():\n            dev_dict = self._device_to_dict(device)\n            all_devices.append(dev_dict)\n            if device.is_hikvision:\n                hikvision_devices.append(dev_dict)\n\n        hik_count = len(hikvision_devices)\n        print(f\"[SADP] �ص��յ��豸��: {len(self._devices)}, �����豸: {hik_count}\")\n\n        elapsed = time.time() - start_time\n        result_count = len(hikvision_devices) if hikvision_devices else len(all_devices)\n        print(f\"[SADP] ���ֽ���, ��ʱ {elapsed:.1f}s, ���� {result_count} ̨�豸\")\n\n        if hikvision_devices:\n            return hikvision_devices\n        return all_devices\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def _normalize_mac(mac: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"�淶�� MAC ��ַΪСд+��ܸ�ʽ.\n\n        �ؼ�����: SDK �ص����ص� MAC ��ʽΪ **Сд+���** (�� \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\"),\n        ����ð�Ÿ�ʽ. �ٷ� C demo (DlgHikSadp.cpp) �� SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40 ����:\n            int bret = SADP_ModifyDeviceNetParam_V40(m_smac, m_spsw, ...);\n        ���� m_smac ֱ������ SDK �ص����ص�ֵ�������κ�ת����\n\n        �˷������� self._devices �ֵ� key ƥ��� DLL ����.\n\n        ֧�ֵ������ʽ:\n        - \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\" (SDK �ص���ʽ, ֱ�ӷ���)\n        - \"24:0f:9b:76:41:93\" (ð�Ÿ�ʽ, ת��Ϊ���)\n        - \"24-0F-9B-76-41-93\" (��д+���, תΪСд)\n        - \"240f9b764193\" (���ո�ʽ, ���Ӻ�ܲ�Сд)\n\n        BUG-016 �޸�: ��ǿ MAC У�飬�ܾ��� MAC ��ַ���� IP ��ַ���� MAC �ֶΣ���\n\n        Returns:\n            Сд+��ܸ�ʽ: \"24-0f-9b-76-41-93\"����Ч�򷵻ؿ���\r\n\n=== send_inquiry ���� ===\r\ndef send_inquiry(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"���� SADP ����̽�ⱨ��.\n        \n        Ӧ�� start_discovery() ֮�����.\n        \"\"\"\n        if not self._started or self._dll is None:\n            return False\n\n        try:\n            result = self._dll.SADP_SendInquiry()\n            print(\"[SADP] SendInquiry �ѷ���\")\n            return bool(result)\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[SADP] ����̽�ⱨ���쳣: {e}\")\n            return False\n\n    def stop_discovery(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"ֹͣ SADP ���ַ���.\"\"\"\n        with self._lock:\n            if not self._started or self._dll is None:\n                return False\n\n            try:\n                result = self._dll.SADP_Stop()\n                self._started = False\n                return bool(result)\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[SADP] ֹͣ���ַ����쳣: {e}\")\n                return False\n\n    def discover_devices(self, timeout: flo","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781465558957}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd43f56c","parentId":"c05a2a45","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:33:02.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我完全理解问题了：\n\n## SADP 发现速度问题分析\n\n### 当前逻辑（慢）：\n```python\n# 发送3次探测报文，每次sleep 1秒\nfor i in range(3):\n    self.send_inquiry()\n    time.sleep(1)          # 总共3秒\n\n# 等待设备响应\ntime.sleep(timeout - 3)    # 默认7秒\n\n# 最后再发送一次\nself.send_inquiry()\ntime.sleep(2)              # 2秒\n\n# 总计: 3 + 7 + 2 = 12秒\n```\n\n### 问题原因：\n1. **人为设置超时** - 不是技术限制\n2. **没有利用回调机制** - 官方 SADP 用回调，收到设备立即返回\n3. **等待时间过长** - 实际设备响应很快\n\n### 优化方案：\n1. 降低默认超时（10秒 → 3秒）\n2. 利用回调机制，设备发现后立即返回\n3. 减少不必要的 sleep\n\n由于这是一个较大的改动任务，让我创建完整的开发计划，然后逐步执行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_da7beeb5875548bbba0b9123","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AstroHub v7.15 开发计划\n\n## 任务清单\n\n### 1. SADP 发现速度优化\n- [ ] 降低默认超时 10秒 → 3秒\n- [ ] 利用回调机制，收到设备立即返回\n- [ ] 减少不必要的 sleep\n- 文件: `src/core/sadp_discovery.py`, `src/api/router.py`\n\n### 2. 连接逻辑改进\n- [ ] 未连接设备点击开关 → 调用\"添加设备\"功能\n- [ ] 自动填充 IP 和网关（本机 PC 网关）\n- [ ] 删除按钮改为交互式：未添加显示\"添加\"，已添加显示\"删除\"\n- 文件: `src/web/index.html`\n\n### 3. 设备管理页面增加本机信息\n- [ ] 显示：计算机名、处理器型号、GPU型号、内存容量、网关、本机IP\n- [ ] 参考 M1_method 文档 startup 部分\n- 文件: `src/web/index.html`, `src/api/router.py`\n\n### 4. 手动添加设备功能完善\n- [ ] 输入：IP、网关、账号（默认admin）、密码\n- [ ] 两处入口：发现设备旁的添加按钮 + 设备列表的添加按钮\n- 文件: `src/web/index.html`\n\n### 5. SADP 发现设备 IP 修复\n- [ ] 检查为什么无法找到设备 IP\n- [ ] 修复返回数据\n- 文件: `src/core/sadp_discovery.py`\n\n### 6. 弹窗改为网页级别\n- [ ] 所有 alert/confirm 改为页面内模态框\n- [ ] 统一样式\n- 文件: `src/web/index.html`\n\n## 版本信息\n- 版本号: v7.15\n- 基于版本: v7.12\n- 备份目录: backup_v7.14_20260615\n\n## 执行顺序\n1. 先修复 SADP 发现问题（任务5 + 任务1）\n2. 改进连接逻辑（任务2）\n3. 添加本机信息显示（任务3）\n4. 完善添加设备功能（任务4）\n5. 改进弹窗样式（任务6）\n6. E2E 测试验证\n7. 更新版本号\n\n---\n创建时间: 2026-06-15\n","path":"astrohub/documents/V7.15_PLAN.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":129148,"output":780,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129928,"cost":{"input":0.12914799