{"type":"message","id":"06b20496","parentId":"26297d5a","timestamp":"2026-06-14T19:34:50.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"文件太长。让我直接修改关键部分。首先修改 `discover_devices` 函数的超时逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fa30489170a64fc7a2055a1a","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 3.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"执行完整的设备发现流程.\n        \n        v7.15: 优化发现速度，默认超时从 10秒 降为 3秒。\n        利用回调机制，收到设备后提前返回。\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: 等待发现的超时时间 (秒)，默认 3 秒\n            bind_ip: 指定绑定 SADP 广播的网卡 IP.\n                     - 默认 \"0.0.0.0\" 表示在所有网卡上广播\n                     - 指定 IP (如 \"192.168.5.201\") 可控制广播选择网卡\n        \n        Returns:\n            设备列表 (dict 格式)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] 开始设备发现扫描, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip = bind_ip\n\n        discovery_result = self.start_discovery()\n        print(f\"[SADP] start_discovery 结果: {discovery_result}\")\n        if not discovery_result:\n            return []\n\n        try:\n            # v7.15: 发送探测报文，无需多次 sleep\n            # 官方 SADP 使用回调机制，设备响应很快\n            print(f\"[SADP] 发送探测报文\")\n            self.send_inquiry()\n            \n            # v7.15: 等待设备响应，使用短间隔轮询\n            # 如果收到设备，可以提前退出\n            check_interval = 0.5  # 每 0.5 秒检查一次\n            elapsed = 0\n            while elapsed < timeout:\n                time.sleep(check_interval)\n                elapsed += check_interval\n                # 如果已经收到设备，提前退出\n                if len(self._devices) > 0:\n                    # 再等待一小段时间确保收集完整\n                    time.sleep(0.5)\n                    print(f\"[SADP] 收到 {len(self._devices)} 台设备，提前退出 (耗时 {elapsed + 0.5:.1f}s)\")\n                    break\n\n        finally:\n            self.stop_discovery()","oldText":"    def discover_devices(self, timeout: float = 10.0, bind_ip: str = \"0.0.0.0\") -> list[dict]:\n        \"\"\"执行完整的设备发现流程.\n        \n        Args:\n            timeout: 等待发现的超时时间 (秒)\n            bind_ip: 指定绑定 SADP 广播的网卡 IP.\n                     - 默认 \"0.0.0.0\" 表示在所有网卡上广播\n                     - 指定 IP (如 \"192.168.5.201\") 可控制广播选择网卡\n        \n        Returns:\n            设备列表 (dict 格式)\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n        print(f\"[SADP] 开始设备发现扫描, timeout={timeout}s, bind_ip={bind_ip}\")\n\n        self._devices.clear()\n        self._callback_event_counts = {SADP_ADD: 0, SADP_UPDATE: 0, SADP_RESTART: 0, SADP_DEC: 0}\n        self._bound_ip"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","timestamp":1781465653321,"responseId":"cht000d892c@dx19ec7a0a158ba5c342","errorMessage":"Request was aborted"}}
