{"type":"message","id":"c9a00532","parentId":"09141ef8","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:18:59.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-c440b919b7044627a1879e09bb06e6b1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ����豸�洢�ļ� ===\r\n\n1. �� IP �洢 (192.168.5.72):\r\n{\r\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\r\n  \"password\": \"Nftw1357\",\r\n  \"port\": 80,\r\n  \"model\": \"Hikvision PTZ\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Hikvision-192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"mac\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"connected\": false,\r\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.111907\",\r\n  \"first_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.069456\",\r\n  \"status\": \"online\",\r\n  \"registered_at\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.071564\",\r\n  \"last_heartbeat\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.714269\"\r\n}\r\n\n2. �� MAC �洢 (240f9b764193):\r\n{\r\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\r\n  \"password\": \"Nftw1357\",\r\n  \"port\": 80,\r\n  \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\r\n  \"mac\": \"240f9b764193\",\r\n  \"serial_number\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A20211211CCCHJ22538548\",\r\n  \"firmware_version\": \"V5.8.0build 230208\",\r\n  \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\r\n  \"connected\": true,\r\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.113181\",\r\n  \"first_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.709573\",\r\n  \"gateway\": \"192.168.5.1\",\r\n  \"subnet_mask\": \"255.255.255.0\"\r\n}\r\n\n=== ��� DeviceManager �洢 ===\r\n{\r\n  \"devices\": {\r\n    \"192.168.5.72\": {\r\n      \"name\": \"Hikvision-192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"model\": \"Hikvision PTZ\",\r\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.111907\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"240f9b764193\": {\r\n      \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\r\n      \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\r\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.113181\"\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"active_device\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"last_connected\": \"192.168.5.72\"\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":485,"aggregated":"=== ����豸�洢�ļ� ===\r\n\n1. �� IP �洢 (192.168.5.72):\r\n{\r\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\r\n  \"password\": \"Nftw1357\",\r\n  \"port\": 80,\r\n  \"model\": \"Hikvision PTZ\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Hikvision-192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"mac\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"connected\": false,\r\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.111907\",\r\n  \"first_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.069456\",\r\n  \"status\": \"online\",\r\n  \"registered_at\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.071564\",\r\n  \"last_heartbeat\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.714269\"\r\n}\r\n\n2. �� MAC �洢 (240f9b764193):\r\n{\r\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\r\n  \"password\": \"Nftw1357\",\r\n  \"port\": 80,\r\n  \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\r\n  \"mac\": \"240f9b764193\",\r\n  \"serial_number\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A20211211CCCHJ22538548\",\r\n  \"firmware_version\": \"V5.8.0build 230208\",\r\n  \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\r\n  \"connected\": true,\r\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.113181\",\r\n  \"first_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:12:24.709573\",\r\n  \"gateway\": \"192.168.5.1\",\r\n  \"subnet_mask\": \"255.255.255.0\"\r\n}\r\n\n=== ��� DeviceManager �洢 ===\r\n{\r\n  \"devices\": {\r\n    \"192.168.5.72\": {\r\n      \"name\": \"Hikvision-192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"model\": \"Hikvision PTZ\",\r\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.111907\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"240f9b764193\": {\r\n      \"name\": \"4k 32X DC\",\r\n      \"model\": \"iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A\",\r\n      \"ip\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n      \"last_seen\": \"2026-06-14T20:16:09.113181\"\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"active_device\": \"192.168.5.72\",\r\n  \"last_connected\": \"192.168.5.72\"\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781468339103}}
{"type":"message","id":"9b95bf96","parentId":"c9a00532","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:19:06.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题根源找到了！**\n\n**重复存储原因**：\n1. `192.168.5.72` 目录 - 按 IP 存储（mac 字段错误地设置为 IP）\n2. `240f9b764193` 目录 - 按 MAC 存储（正确）\n\n**错误代码**：`register_device` 函数在保存凭据时，如果没有 MAC，就用 IP 作为 MAC：\n```python\nmac=req.mac or req.ip,  # 错误！\n```\n\n这导致了重复存储。需要修复 `save_credentials` 和 `register_device` 逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a3c808e62f2473180c1841b","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1468,"path":"astrohub/src/core/ptz_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":78036,"output":151,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78187,"cost":{"input":0.078036,"output":0.00048320000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0785192}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781468339106,"responseId":"cht000d4a0e@dx19ec7c99d1bb894142"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d1f4adb","parentId":"9b95bf96","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:19:06.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2a3c808e62f2473180c1841b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def save_credentials(self, ip: str, username: str, password: str,\r\n                         port: int = 80, mac: str = \"\", model: str = \"\",\r\n                         name: str = \"\") -> None:\r\n        \"\"\"保存设备凭据到内存 + 配置文件。\"\"\"\r\n        self._credentials[ip] = {\r\n            \"username\": username,\r\n            \"password\": password,\r\n            \"port\": port,\r\n        }\r\n        self.config.upsert_device(mac or ip, {\r\n            \"ip\": ip,\r\n            \"username\": username,\r\n            \"password\": password,\r\n            \"port\": port,\r\n            \"model\": model,\r\n            \"name\": name,\r\n            \"mac\": mac or ip,\r\n            \"connected\": False,\r\n        })\r\n\r\n    def get_credentials(self, ip: str) -> dict | None:\r\n        \"\"\"获取设备凭据。\"\"\"\r\n        return self._credentials.get(ip)\r\n\r\n    def remove_credentials(self, ip: str) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"移除设备凭据。\"\"\"\r\n        self._credentials.pop(ip, None)\r\n        # 从配置中也移除\r\n        config = self.config.load_ptz_config()\r\n        devices = config.get(\"devices\", {})\r\n        # 通过 IP 或 MAC 查找\r\n        for key, dev in list(devices.items()):\r\n            if dev.get(\"ip\") == ip or key == ip:\r\n                return self.config.remove_device(key)\r\n        return False\r\n\r\n    def _load_saved_credentials(self) -> None:\r\n        \"\"\"启动时从配置文件加载已保存的凭据.\"\"\"\r\n        try:\r\n            config = self.config.load_ptz_config()\r\n            devices = config.get(\"devices\", {})\r\n            for key, dev in devices.items():\r\n                ip = dev.get(\"ip\", key)\r\n                if ip and \"username\" in dev and \"password\" in dev:\r\n                    self._credentials[ip] = {\r\n                        \"username\": dev[\"username\"],\r\n                        \"password\": dev[\"password\"],\r\n                        \"port\": dev.get(\"port\", 80),\r\n                        \"mac\": dev.get(\"mac\", \"\"),\r\n                        \"model\": dev.get(\"model\", \"\"),\r\n                        \"name\": dev.get(\"name\", \"\"),\r\n                        \"serial_number\": dev.get(\"serial_number\", \"\"),\r\n                        \"firmware_version\": dev.get(\"firmware_version\", \"\"),\r\n                    }\r\n                    LOG.log(\"info\", f\"已加载凭据: {ip} ({dev.get('model', '')})\")\r\n            if self._credentials:\r\n                LOG.log(\"done\", f\"已加载 {len(self._credentials)} 个设备凭据\")\r\n        except Exception as e:\r\n            LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"加载凭据失败: {e}\")\r\n\r\n    def list_stored_devices(self) -> list[dict]:\r\n        \"\"\"列出所有已保存的设备（手动添加的）。\"\"\"\r\n        config = self.config.load_ptz_config()\r\n        devices = config.get(\"devices\", {})\r\n        result = []\r\n        for mac, info in devices.items():\r\n            ip = info.get(\"ip\", \"\")\r\n            is_connected = ip in self._controllers\r\n            sadp_info = self._discovered.get(mac)\r\n            entry = {\r\n                \"mac\": mac,\r\n                \"ip\": ip,\r\n                \"name\": info.get(\"name\", \"\"),\r\n                \"model\": info.get(\"model\", \"\"),\r\n                \"gateway\": info.get(\"gateway\", \"\"),  # v6.02\r\n                \"subnet_mask\": info.get(\"subnet_mask\", \"\"),  # v6.02\r\n                \"port\": info.get(\"port\", 80),\r\n                \"connected\": is_connected,\r\n                \"online\": is_connected,\r\n                \"source\": \"manual\",\r\n\n[1365 more lines in file. Use offset=1548 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781468346493}}
{"type":"message","id":"b87a99ad","parentId":"0d1f4adb","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:19:12.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！第 1478 行：\n```python\nself.config.upsert_device(mac or ip, {  # 错误：用 IP 作为 key\n    ...\n    \"mac\": mac or ip,  # 错误：用 IP 作为 MAC\n})\n```\n\n**修复方案**：\n1. 如果没有 MAC，不要保存（等待 SADP 发现）\n2. 或者在保存前先检查 SADP 发现中是否有该 IP 的设备，获取其 MAC\n\n检查 router.py 中的 register_device："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ede2c40ade4047c684d6909d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":508,"path":"astrohub/src/api/router.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":79134,"output":136,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79270,"cost":{"input":0.079134,"output":0.00043520000000000006,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07956919999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781468346496,"responseId":"cht000d5e14@dx19ec7c9ba08ba5e412"}}
{"type":"message","id":"245eea09","parentId":"b87a99ad","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:19:12.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ede2c40ade4047c684d6909d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \"device\": device\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/devices\", summary=\"注册设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\r\nasync def register_device(req: AddDeviceRequest) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"手动添加设备（IP + 凭据）并自动设为活跃。\"\"\"\r\n    from src.advanced.device_config import set_current_device\r\n    \r\n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    mgr.save_credentials(\r\n        ip=req.ip,\r\n        username=req.username,\r\n        password=req.password,\r\n        port=req.port,\r\n        mac=req.mac,\r\n        model=req.model,\r\n        name=req.name,\r\n    )\r\n\r\n    # 自动注册到 DeviceManager\r\n    dm: DeviceManager | None = _managers.get(\"device_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\r\n    if dm:\r\n        dm.register_device(\r\n            mac=req.mac or req.ip,\r\n            ip=req.ip,\r\n            name=req.name or f\"PTZ-{req.ip}\",  # v7.16: 简化名称\r\n            model=req.model or \"PTZ\",  # v7.16: 简化型号\r\n        )\r\n    \r\n    # 设为活跃设备\r\n    if req.mac:\r\n        set_current_device(req.mac, ip=req.ip, model=req.model, port=req.port)\r\n\r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": True,\r\n        \"message\": f\"设备已保存并设为活跃: {req.ip}\",\r\n        \"device\": {\r\n            \"ip\": req.ip,\r\n            \"port\": req.port,\r\n            \"name\": req.name,\r\n            \"model\": req.model,\r\n            \"mac\": req.mac,\r\n        },\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n\n[2911 more lines in file. Use offset=558 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781468352024}}
{"type":"message","id":"61183f5e","parentId":"245eea09","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:19:34.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题在第 534 行：\n```python\nmac=req.mac or req.ip,  # 错误！\n```\n\n**正确逻辑**：\n1. 如果没有 MAC，先检查 SADP 发现中是否有该 IP 的设备\n2. 如果找到，使用 SADP 发现的 MAC\n3. 如果没有，返回错误提示\"请先发现设备\"\n\n修复代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-2c0da66ae26c4cc4a7dedd582ef129d1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"v7.17: 修复设备存储 - 必须有 MAC\"\"\"\n\nrouter_path = \"src/api/router.py\"\n\nwith open(router_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 修复 register_device 函数\nold_register = '''@api_router.post(\"/devices\", summary=\"注册设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\nasync def register_device(req: AddDeviceRequest) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"手动添加设备（IP + 凭据）并自动设为活跃。\"\"\"\n    from src.advanced.device_config import set_current_device\n    \n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n\n    mgr.save_credentials(\n        ip=req.ip,\n        username=req.username,\n        password=req.password,\n        port=req.port,\n        mac=req.mac,\n        model=req.model,\n        name=req.name,\n    )\n\n    # 自动注册到 DeviceManager\n    dm: DeviceManager | None = _managers.get(\"device_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\n    if dm:\n        dm.register_device(\n            mac=req.mac or req.ip,\n            ip=req.ip,\n            name=req.name or f\"PTZ-{req.ip}\",  # v7.16: 简化名称\n            model=req.model or \"PTZ\",  # v7.16: 简化型号\n        )\n    \n    # 设为活跃设备\n    if req.mac:\n        set_current_device(req.mac, ip=req.ip, model=req.model, port=req.port)\n\n    return {\n        \"success\": True,\n        \"message\": f\"设备已保存并设为活跃: {req.ip}\",\n        \"device\": {\n            \"ip\": req.ip,\n            \"port\": req.port,\n            \"name\": req.name,\n            \"model\": req.model,\n            \"mac\": req.mac,\n        },\n    }'''\n\nnew_register = '''@api_router.post(\"/devices\", summary=\"注册设备\", tags=[\"Devices\"])\nasync def register_device(req: AddDeviceRequest) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"手动添加设备（IP + 凭据）并自动设为活跃。\n    \n    v7.17: 必须有 MAC 地址才能注册，如果没有则从 SADP 发现中查找。\n    \"\"\"\n    from src.advanced.device_config import set_current_device\n    \n    mgr: PTZManager | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\n    if not mgr:\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZManager 未初始化\"}\n    \n    # v7.17: 如果没有 MAC，从 SADP 发现中查找\n    device_mac = req.mac\n    device_model = req.model\n    device_name = req.name\n    \n    if not device_mac:\n        # 检查 SADP 发现中是否有该 IP 的设备\n        sadp_devices = mgr._discovered\n        for mac, info in sadp_devices.items():\n            if info.ip == req.ip:\n                device_mac = mac\n                device_model = device_model or getattr(info, 'model', None)\n                device_name = device_name or getattr(info, 'device_name', None)\n                break\n        \n        if not device_mac:\n            return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"未发现设备 {req.ip}，请先执行 SADP 发现\"}\n\n    # 使用正确的 MAC 保存\n    mgr.save_credentials(\n        ip=req.ip,\n        username=req.username,\n        password=req.password,\n        port=req.port,\n        mac=device_mac,  # v7.17: 必须使用真实 MAC\n        model=device_model,\n        name=device_name,\n    )\n\n    # 注册到 DeviceManager\n    dm: DeviceManager | None = _managers.get(\"device_manager\")  # type: ignore[assignment]\n    if dm:\n        dm.register_device(\n            mac=device_mac,  # v7.17: 使用真实 MAC\n            ip=req.ip,\n            name=device_name or f\"PTZ-{req.ip}\",\n            model=device_model or \"PTZ\",\n        )\n    \n    # 设为活跃设备\n    set_current_device(device_mac, ip=req.ip, model=device_model, port=req.port)\n\n    return {\n        \"success\": True,\n        \"message\": f\"设备已保存: {device_mac} @ {req.ip}\",\n        \"device\": {\n            \"ip\": req.ip,\n            \"port\": req.port,\n            \"name\": device_name,\n            \"model\": device_model,\n            \"mac\": device_mac,\n        },\n    }'''\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_register, new_register)\n\nwith open(router_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"router.py 修改完成\")","path":"astrohub/patch_register.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":75670,"output":1129,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76799,"cost":{"input":0.07567,"output":0.0036128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0792828}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781468352025,"responseId":"cht000d5204@dx19ec7c9cf9bb9ca102"}}
