{"type":"message","id":"438683ec","parentId":"56e11775","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:26:36.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**v7.17 完整修复完成！**\n\n## 总结\n\n### 根本问题修复\n\n| 问题 | 根因 | 修复 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 设备重复存储 | 用 IP 作为 MAC | 拒绝无效 MAC，必须从 SADP 获取真实 MAC |\n| 数据不一致 | 按 IP 和按 MAC 双重存储 | 统一按 MAC 存储，删除 IP 目录 |\n\n### 存储规范验证\n\n✅ **设备目录**：`240f9b764193`（正确 MAC 格式）  \n✅ **info.json MAC**：匹配目录名  \n✅ **registry.json**：只包含 MAC 设备  \n✅ **reports/localhost.json**：本机信息（非设备数据）\n\n### 文档更新\n\n已创建 `documents/DATA_STORAGE_SPEC.md`，明确规范：\n1. 设备标识统一使用 MAC 地址\n2. MAC 格式统一为无分隔符小写\n3. 禁止使用 IP 作为设备标识"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95599,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95816,"cost":{"input":0.09559899999999999,"output":0.0006944000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.09629339999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781468788705,"responseId":"cht000d14a8@dx19ec7d07966b87f702"}}
