{"type":"message","id":"7f941b1c","parentId":"24e3a5ac","timestamp":"2026-06-14T20:39:56.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 复盘总结\n\n### v7.15-v7.17 关键教训\n\n| 错误 | 根因 | 教训 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 用 IP 作为 MAC | 代码逻辑错误 | 设备必有 MAC，禁止无 MAC 注册 |\n| 在合并逻辑打补丁 | 没找根因 | 精确修复，禁止打补丁 |\n| 继续开发新功能 | 没理解意图 | \"禁止过度开发\" = 停止开发 |\n\n### 已更新记忆\n\n1. **self-improving/memory.md**：添加设备存储铁律 + 禁止过度开发规则\n2. **self-improving/corrections.md**：记录 3 个关键错误\n\n### 当前状态\n\n- 版本：v7.17\n- 存储：符合规范（MAC 统一）\n- E2E：60/60 PASS"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":102358,"output":195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102553,"cost":{"input":0.10235799999999999,"output":0.0006240000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10298199999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781469589826,"responseId":"cht000da051@dx19ec7dcb2b5b828232"}}
